column16: Aaron Judge grounds into a double play, pitcher Rob Zastryzny to second baseman Javier Baez to first baseman Anthony Rizzo.   Starlin Castro out at 2nd.
Starlin Castro singles on a sharp line drive to left fielder Jon Jay.
Aaron Hicks homers (6) on a fly ball to center field.   Rob Refsnyder scores.    Brett Gardner scores.
Brett Gardner singles on a ground ball to left fielder Jon Jay.   Rob Refsnyder to 2nd.
Chris Carter flies out sharply to right fielder Ben Zobrist.
Didi Gregorius walks.   Starlin Castro to 2nd.
Gary Sanchez pops out to shortstop Addison Russell in foul territory.
Aaron Judge flies out to center fielder Albert Almora.
Aaron Hicks grounds into a double play, pitcher Rob Zastryzny to second baseman Javier Baez to first baseman Anthony Rizzo.   Jordan Montgomery out at 2nd.
Brett Gardner lines out to center fielder Albert Almora.
Chris Carter grounds out, second baseman Javier Baez to first baseman Anthony Rizzo.
